reviews.review_msg: I've had the pleasure of being in Imran's class 3 times over my university career and he is one of the intelligent and most insightful individuals I know. He's laid back, but he's also very knowledgeable TA's I've ever met, not to mention he is the nicest guy ever. If you get him, take the time to talk to him, cuz he's got some amazing stories!
